and we ended up on this deserted island.

406
00:24:14,480 --> 00:24:17,660
I am the most beautiful
creature in the world.

407
00:24:15,520 --> 00:24:22,350
[Otohime's plot draws near!!]

408
00:24:17,660 --> 00:24:20,690
I am Otohime, the ruler of Ryugu.

409
00:24:22,740 --> 00:24:27,440
My worst summer vacation
